Variations. Specimens from Cyrenaica in Lybia often show more blue green reflexions, the punctation is often finer (
Fig. 10
), and the body size is smaller ( 5 mm ) than specimens from other regions.

Distribution. Along the Mediterranean coast from southern France (Montpellier) to southern Spain , in North Africa from Morocco to the Sinai (
Fig. 13
).
